    dc:description "FIGURE 54. Global diversity and distribution of the subgenus Mycale (Carmia) based on data derived from the World Porifera Database 2020 combined with the new data from the present study. The map presents the number of species found in each of the Marine Ecoregions of the World (Spalding et al. 2007)." ;
